[I] Memory Enhancement Game

[T] Blinken uses a special handwriting font called Steve that is in the fonts
[T] directory to show the status text. If this font is not currently installed
[T] on the target system, on first run Blinken uses the fonts:/ ioslave to copy
[T] it to the user's fonts location.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/blinken/

